'''雙態性真菌'''是一组在不同环境温度下改变其形态的真菌，绝大多数属于[[阿耶洛双态菌科|阿耶洛双态菌科]]。<ref name="Jiang" /> 这些真菌在环境温度下以[[黴菌|黴菌]]/[[菌絲|菌絲]]/的絲狀形态繁殖 <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kcom.edu/faculty/chamberlain/website/LECTS/Fungi.htm |title=Fungi |accessdate=2009-06-06 |format= |work= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090606075938/http://www.kcom.edu/faculty/chamberlain/website/LECTS/Fungi.htm#di|archivedate=2009-06-06 }}</ref>，在人体或高温培养条件下则以孤立的[[酵母|酵母]]形式芽生繁殖。一個例子就是导致[[艾滋病|艾滋病]]患者[[机会性感染|机会性感染]]的[[新埃蒙斯菌属|新埃蒙斯菌属]]: 在[[室溫|室溫]]下，它作為一個黴菌生長，在[[體溫|體溫]]下，它作為一個酵母生長。<ref name="Jiang">{{cite book |last=Jiang, Y., Dukik, K., Muñoz, J.F. et al. |title=Phylogeny, ecology and taxonomy of systemic pathogens and their relatives in Ajellomycetaceae (Onygenales): Blastomyces, Emergomyces, Emmonsia, Emmonsiellopsis. Fungal Diversity 90, 245–291 (2018). |url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2Fs13225-018-0403-y#citeas |access-date=2021-03-09 |archive-date=2021-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411163733/https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s13225-018-0403-y#citeas |dead-url=no }}</ref>

