== 雙態性真菌的生態學 ==
一些物種是人類和其他動物重要的病原體，包括[[阿耶洛双态菌科|阿耶洛双态菌科]]的[[粗球孢子菌|粗球孢子菌]] <ref name=DF>{{cite web |url=http://pathmicro.med.sc.edu/mycology/mycology-6.htm |title=Dimorphic Fungi |accessdate=2007-08-19 |work= |archive-date=2007-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070818135315/http://pathmicro.med.sc.edu/mycology/mycology-6.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，{{link-en|副球孢子菌屬|Paracoccidioides}}，[[芽生孢子菌属|芽生孢子菌属]]（''Blastomyces dermatitidis''），[[莢膜組織胞漿菌|莢膜組織胞漿菌]]（''Histoplasma capsulatum''）和[[新埃蒙斯菌属|新埃蒙斯菌属]]等。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Kenyon, et al|title=A Dimorphic Fungus Causing Disseminated Infection in South Africa|journal=The New England Journal of Medicine|date=October 10, 2013|issue=N Engl J Med 2013; 369:1416-1424|doi=10.1056/NEJMoa1215460|url=http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMoa1215460|accessdate=October 10, 2013|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411163815/https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMoa1215460|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{cite book|last=Klein BS, Tebbets B.|title=Dimorphism and virulence in fungi. Curr Opin Microbiol. 2007;10(4):314-319. doi:10.1016/j.mib.2007.04.002|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3412142/|access-date=2021-03-09|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411163750/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3412142/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 其它菌种如[[申克氏孢子絲菌|申克氏孢子絲菌]]（''Sporothrix schenckii''），[[馬爾尼菲青黴菌|馬爾尼菲青黴菌]]，[[曲霉属|曲霉属]]，[[隐球菌属|隐球菌属]]以及某些[[植物|植物]]病原體[[玉米黑粉菌|玉米黑粉菌]]（''Ustilago maydis'') 和芝士制真菌白地黴（''Geotrichum candidum''）也具有雙態性生命週期。

